            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-12-31T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-06-25T11:00:00-05:00" n="255" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d255">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In a statement issued to the press on August 17, the United States Government
                    expressed concern regarding Hungarian electoral abuses and requested the end of
                    unwarranted disfranchisements. For the text of the statement, see Department of
                    State <hi rend="italic">Bidletm</hi>, August 24, 1947, page 392. A similar
                    statement was issued by the British Government.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
